articles.description: Zane Waterman tossed in 28 points, Zavier Turner scored 25 and Pauly Paulicap chipped in with a double-double to propel Manhattan to a 93-76 victory over Monmouth on Saturday night.
articles.headline: Waterman, Turner lead Manhattan over Monmouth 93-76

articles.description: Denzel Mahoney had 27 points, including a game-tying 3-pointer at the end of regulation, and Southeast Missouri State beat Tennessee-Martin 81-77 in overtime on Saturday night.
articles.headline: SE Missouri State beats Tenn.-Martin 81-77 in OT

articles.description: Shannon Bogues scored a career-best 35 points, making 6 of 8 from long range, as Stephen F. Austin thrashed Northwestern State 97-50 on Saturday night.
articles.headline: Bogues scores 35 as SF Austin romps past NW State 97-50

articles.description: Branden Johnson scored 14 points and grabbed 12 rebounds and Alabama State extended its winning streak to three games, beating Alabama A&M 69-50 on Saturday night.
articles.headline: Alabama State beats Alabama A&M 69-50

articles.description: Miye Oni's 19 points helps Yale to critical two-win Ivy League weekend
articles.headline: Yale completes Ivy League back-to-back weekend sweep  - Via Ivy League

images.caption: Miye Oni's 19 points helps Yale to critical two-win Ivy League weekend
images.name: Yale completes Ivy League back-to-back weekend sweep  - Via Ivy League

articles.description: Dante Sterling scored a career-high 29 points, A.J. Mosby scored 22 points and Alcorn State downed Mississippi Valley State 94-90 in overtime Saturday night.
articles.headline: Mississippi Valley St. outlasts Alcorn St. 94-90 in OT

videos.description: Emmanuel Akot finds DeAndre Ayton in transition and he finishes with a two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Arizona's Akot feeds Ayton for sweet slam

videos.description: Dusan Ristic shows patience, spins around three Cal defenders, knocks in a tough basket and gets fouled on the play.
videos.headline: Arizona's Ristic gets through traffic for basket and-1

videos.description: Emmanuel Akot connects with Allonzo Trier who knocks in an unbelievably long triple for the Wildcats.
videos.headline: Arizona's Trier hits deep 3

videos.description: Deandre Ayton elevates to receive the lob from Parker Jackson-Cartwright and finishes with a two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Arizona's Jackson-Cartwright connects with Ayton for mean alley-oop slam

videos.description: Allonzo Trier drives to the rim but he's denied by Kingsley Okoroh who puts both arms up to stop the basket.
videos.headline: Cal's Okoroh rises up for strong block

videos.description: Parker Jackson-Cartwright gets a strong defensive board, dishes to Allonzo Trier who speeds down the court and glides up in the air for an easy layup.
videos.headline: Arizona's Trier hits a beautiful layup in transition
